'''''Veed''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] which served in the [[Airam sector/Legends|Airam sector]].

When the decision was made to construct a Rebel shipyard in [[Airam (group)|Airam]] space, ''Veed'' was assigned to the convoy which would bring the needed supplies and personnel. ''Veed'' itself held troops which would be used as defense and security. However, the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] learned of them. It [[Battle of Rocrin|ambushed]] the convoy in the [[Rocrin system/Legends|Rocrin system]]. ''Veed'', along with the other Rebel ships, was destroyed.

